ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The common feature of all these reports is that no viral (or non-viral)
infectious agent that is unequivocally associated with these outbreaks has
yet been isolated. The wide geographic spread of the reports and the
almost apparently exclusive involvement of hospital staff (and travellers) are
singular features of this enigmatic situation. 2 reports suggest that the
infection may have reached Taiwan also. - Mod.CP]
